9/13/2024: Project committed.
  Features:
    -Pixelated canvas that can be resized by the user from 1px to 8px in height and length.
    -Pixels can be navigated around by the ARROW keys on the keyboard.
    -Pixel selection marker can be changed between outline, highlight, both, and none.
    -Image can be downloaded with a user chosen name.
    -3-color-palette that can be customized by selecting an individual color and change the rgb slider values in the animated pop-up.
    -Clicking the ENTER key on the keyboard flips through the 3-color-palette.
